<subSubSection id="C320B6A37A584A71FF52F8CDD8A9F8C2" box="[170,650,1805,1825]" pageId="5" pageNumber="1051" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="8B85E5287A584A71FF52F8CDD8A9F8C2" blockId="5.[170,650,1805,1825]" box="[170,650,1805,1825]" pageId="5" pageNumber="1051">Etym.: chailluzii (Latin), after Forêt du Chailluz.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C320B6A37A584A71FF72F8F9DE88FF3C" pageId="5" pageNumber="1051" type="description">
<paragraph id="8B85E5287A584A71FF72F8F9DE88FF3C" blockId="5.[138,777,1849,2000]" lastBlockId="5.[824,1463,178,303]" pageId="5" pageNumber="1051">
Pileo 
<quantity id="4CC248CD7A584A71FF45F8F9DB03F8A8" box="[189,288,1849,1867]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.15" metricValueMax="6.5" metricValueMin="3.8" pageId="5" pageNumber="1051" unit="mm" value="51.5" valueMax="65.0" valueMin="38.0">38–65 mm</quantity>
lato, hemisphaerico, dein plano-convexo, glutinoso, primo luteo, dein brunneo, margine luteo, KOH ope roseo. Lamellis griseo-violaceis. Stipite 40– 
<date id="FF84C3E87A584A71FE1BF8AED818F863" box="[483,571,1902,1920]" pageId="5" pageNumber="1051" value="1960-10-08" valueMax="1960-10-15" valueMin="1960-10-08">
60 X 
<quantity id="4CC248CD7A584A71FDE9F8AED848F863" box="[529,619,1902,1920]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.15" metricValueMax="1.5" metricValueMin="0.8" pageId="5" pageNumber="1051" unit="mm" value="11.5" valueMax="15.0" valueMin="8.0">8–15 mm</quantity>
</date>
, bulboso, bulbo marginato, pallido, interdum in apice violaceo. Margine bulbi e velo pallido vel brunneo. Facie externa mycelioque albida, KOH ope roseo. Carne albida, sapore miti, odore nullo, KOH ope nullo vel pallido rosea. Sporis amygdaliformibus vel limoniformibus, grosse verrucosis, 9.5– 
<date id="FF84C3E87A584A71FBEBFF0DDE18FF3C" box="[1043,1083,205,223]" pageId="5" pageNumber="1051" value="1910-10">10 X</date>
<quantity id="4CC248CD7A584A71FBC7FF0DDE84FF3C" box="[1087,1191,205,223]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="6.0" metricValueMax="6.5" metricValueMin="5.5" pageId="5" pageNumber="1051" unit="mm" value="6.0" valueMax="6.5" valueMin="5.5">5.5–6.5 µm</quantity>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
